parameters: \nc<Saki>(Alright, let's clean up quickly and head back...)
\nc<Succubus 1>Hm? What's that? Quite a crowd gathering...

\nc<Succubus 2>No way, an event in the park for promotion? Succubus First
Industries, that's bold...

\nc<Succubus 1>We can't lose to them. We're getting attention now because
of the opening effect, but we're still new...

\nc<Succubus 2>Alright, since they've gathered a crowd for us, let's steal
it away. Here goes!
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Aaah! Is that even allowed?! Senpai, what should we do?
\nc<Senpai>Good work, Saki. Just watch from here on.

\nc<Police Officer 1>Stop right there, you're under arrest for illegal
advertising and public indecency.
\nc<Succubus 1>Eeeeh!? They did it too, why are we the only ones...
\nc<Police Officer 2>You lot haven't received permission yet.

\nc<Senpai>And with that, the matter is settled. They'll be banned from
doing business for a while... Any opening effect will be
gone by then.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>I can't believe this is happening.\bustMsgExp[1, 2] And to
think, those people were really police officers. What they
do during work hours...

\nc<Senpai>They probably came under the pretext of enforcement. We were
lucky. Not only did we get to see Saki's squirting show, but
we also preserved social sexual order...

\nc<Senpai>There's no need to be embarrassed. It was truly amazing. I'd
like to make it an official event.
\nc<>After that, Saki and her senpai returned to the company.

\nc<>The rival company that caused the problem was shut down
immediately due to the crackdown...
